=== EVENT_STOWAWAY ===
# id: 33
# title: Stowaway Discovered
# chinese_title: 发现偷渡者
# category: CrewEvent
# mode: starmap

A stowaway is found hiding in the cargo bay — a young refugee from a war-torn system. They look terrified.

* [Take them on as a crew member]
  ~ gain_crew_member
  收留 (shōuliú) — take in
* [Drop them at the next station]
  ~ lose_fuel(2)
  下一站 (xià yī zhàn) — next stop
* [Interrogate them for useful information]
  ~ gain_credits(10)
  审问 (shěnwèn) — interrogate
